title: Not Everyone Enjoys The Classics  (w/ Adrienne Iapalucci & Joe DeRosa)
description: Jay tells a nightmare Air B&B story and gets advice from Adrienne Iapalucci. Jay explains to guest host Joe DeRosa why Bruce Springsteen’s music is awful. Dan, Jay and Christine discuss Rob Gronkowski’s looks.
author: podcasts@siriusxm.com (Comedy Central)
